966
01:11:36,835 --> 01:11:38,275
And now we can all go home!

967
01:11:39,075 --> 01:11:40,675
Cheers! Cheers!

968
01:11:53,275 --> 01:11:53,875
Let's party.

969
01:12:03,395 --> 01:12:06,355
Everything's ready?
Twenty strategic points blocked.

970
01:12:06,435 --> 01:12:08,675
If they cross any of these junctions
they are caught like rats.

971
01:12:09,075 --> 01:12:11,155
They're taking Michelet Boulevard,
they're going to Place Mazard.

972
01:12:11,875 --> 01:12:13,355
Who's on that corner?

973
01:12:13,475 --> 01:12:16,675
Jean-Bat, N 7.
Call him. He will be the opening act.

974
01:12:17,235 --> 01:12:18,755
N 7, Jean-Bat.
You hear me?

975
01:12:20,275 --> 01:12:22,755
Yes, listening.
You're going to be first. You in position?

976
01:12:23,275 --> 01:12:24,275
Yes no problem.

977
01:12:24,675 --> 01:12:25,875
It's our turn now.

978
01:12:29,075 --> 01:12:30,275
It won't fit.

979
01:12:30,675 --> 01:12:31,475
Nag, nag...

980
01:12:32,915 --> 01:12:35,875
Hey Bavarians, how are you
Still in your tractor?

981
01:12:36,435 --> 01:12:39,875
Sorry about the last time.
I forgot the handbrake. That's why I was so slow.

982
01:12:40,435 --> 01:12:42,675
Hey I'm telling you.
It's a lot better now.

983
01:12:43,075 --> 01:12:45,475
Want to do another Tortoise/Hare or you just chicken?

984
01:12:46,435 --> 01:12:49,395
Ok, you Frogs
always got a big mouth

985
01:12:49,515 --> 01:12:52,075
Come on the motorway with me & we'll see!
Did I upset you?

986
01:12:52,515 --> 01:12:54,275
I'm going to blow up your Peugeot!
I did upset you.

987
01:12:54,675 --> 01:12:55,675
I'm sorry, very sorry.

988
01:12:56,275 --> 01:12:58,915
I'll give you another chance,
but I won't bet much this time.

989
01:12:58,995 --> 01:13:03,395
I feel bad taking money from you so easily.
Here you go my baby, 10F.

990
01:13:04,435 --> 01:13:07,675
You're going to pay for your insolence.
Better to be insolent than ridiculous!

991
01:13:10,675 --> 01:13:12,075
I think you over did it a bit.

992
01:13:12,275 --> 01:13:14,275
Not at all,
Tell 7, 8 and 9 to go red.

993
01:13:14,875 --> 01:13:15,875
Jean-Bat, go on red now.

994
01:13:40,275 --> 01:13:43,075
N 10, in position.
N 11, in position.

995
01:13:43,275 --> 01:13:45,675
Perfect. 12 and 13, prepare yourselves.

996
01:13:48,275 --> 01:13:50,875
This is N13,
I've got a small problem.

997
01:13:52,075 --> 01:13:53,875
There are two cops standing at the light.

998
01:13:54,075 --> 01:13:54,475
Shit!

999
01:13:55,075 --> 01:13:55,875
Move them!

1000
01:13:56,275 --> 01:13:59,075
Easy for you to say! They set up home.

1001
01:14:04,275 --> 01:14:06,675
We are nearly there. Sort it out
or we are done for.

1002
01:14:08,515 --> 01:14:10,075
Pollo, let me talk to the cops.

1003
01:14:11,515 --> 01:14:13,475
Excuse me sir, it's for you.

1004
01:14:14,875 --> 01:14:15,355
Hello.

1005
01:14:15,475 --> 01:14:19,075
This is Gibert.
We found a bomb and it's right next to you.

1006
01:14:19,515 --> 01:14:21,475
Where?
In the traffic light.

1007
01:14:22,275 --> 01:14:24,275
Stay calm
we know how to defuse it.

1008
01:14:24,515 --> 01:14:28,275
Listen carefully. Put the key in the light
and make the light turn red.

1009
01:14:28,475 --> 01:14:29,675
It's already red!

1010
01:14:29,875 --> 01:14:32,275
Don't worry about the colour

1011
01:14:32,595 --> 01:14:34,515
...just turn the key to the right!

1012
01:14:34,595 --> 01:14:36,915
Yes, yes, Mr Commissioner.

1013
01:14:45,075 --> 01:14:46,275
We've just passed 12.

1014
01:14:46,675 --> 01:14:48,275
Hurry up! Hurry up!

1015
01:14:49,075 --> 01:14:49,915
Let me do it!

1016
01:14:53,395 --> 01:14:56,075
19 and 20, get ready. 20 is the last.

1017
01:14:56,275 --> 01:14:57,075
I know.

1018
01:15:10,075 --> 01:15:11,275
Are you sure this is the right road?

1019
01:15:11,675 --> 01:15:12,675
It's a shortcut.

1020
01:16:12,635 --> 01:16:16,675
The motorway! They're dead meat.
We have more power.

1021
01:16:55,075 --> 01:16:56,835
What was that fence for Daniel..?

1022
01:16:57,075 --> 01:16:58,675
The motorway isn't finished. It's a dead end.

1023
01:17:01,675 --> 01:17:03,875
The fact that you know that
doesn't reassure me.

1024
01:17:06,275 --> 01:17:08,675
I may look calm to you
but I'm crapping it here..

1025
01:17:08,875 --> 01:17:09,675
Not long.now..

1026
01:17:09,875 --> 01:17:11,475
That's what worries me,
I wanted a long life.

1027
01:17:11,875 --> 01:17:12,475
Ten seconds.

1028
01:17:12,515 --> 01:17:13,675
Squash that rat!

1029
01:17:16,075 --> 01:17:17,475
Stop. There's no bridge!

1030
01:17:17,675 --> 01:17:18,275
Five seconds.

1031
01:17:20,275 --> 01:17:22,475
GO! Trash him! Trash him!

1032
01:17:23,555 --> 01:17:24,835
Let them win Daniel.

1033
01:17:25,075 --> 01:17:27,875
You only bet 10F. I don't want to die for it.

1034
01:17:28,075 --> 01:17:29,475
It's now or never! Hold on!!!

1035
01:17:38,715 --> 01:17:41,275
Excellent, Karl!
We won!

1036
01:17:43,115 --> 01:17:44,475
Are you sure?

1037
01:17:54,115 --> 01:17:55,715
I swear, you scared me to death!

1038
01:17:57,155 --> 01:17:59,715
I really thought
you'd rather die than lose.

1039
01:18:00,275 --> 01:18:02,715
With the tortoise and the hare,
it's always the tortoise who wins!

1040
01:18:04,475 --> 01:18:07,115
Einstein! You know "La Fontaine?"

1041
01:18:08,275 --> 01:18:09,875
That damn shit! Goddamn!

1042
01:18:10,675 --> 01:18:11,475
Damned...

1043
01:18:11,875 --> 01:18:13,075
...shithead!

1044
01:18:16,275 --> 01:18:20,675
The big hare is not happy to be
fucked by the little tortoise.

1045
01:18:21,595 --> 01:18:26,715
Cougar will be happy.
He's wanted to taste hare for a long time.

1046
01:18:27,235 --> 01:18:29,395
Ja, ja...big hare
big hare.

1047
01:18:50,075 --> 01:18:51,275
I'm sorry about this place.

1048
01:18:53,275 --> 01:18:54,075
It's not very romantic.

1049
01:18:55,275 --> 01:18:56,275
But I wanted you so much.

1050
01:18:56,475 --> 01:18:57,275
Truly?

1051
01:18:57,795 --> 01:18:59,075
I was starting to wonder...

1052
01:19:02,875 --> 01:19:03,555
Shall we do it again?

1053
01:19:05,795 --> 01:19:09,275
Later.
We have to go now.

1054
01:19:13,595 --> 01:19:16,275
Daniel, What are you doing?
I've been looking for you for 15 minutes.

1055
01:19:16,835 --> 01:19:18,075
What were you doing in the dark?

1056
01:19:18,475 --> 01:19:19,555
Developing photos.

1057
01:19:19,635 --> 01:19:22,635
This is not the time for photos.
The Commissioner is waiting!

1058
01:19:31,675 --> 01:19:33,195
In the name of the President of the Republic

1059
01:19:33,315 --> 01:19:36,875
..it is my privilege to present to you
the Knight's Order of National Merit.

1060
01:19:44,075 --> 01:19:44,635
Congratulations.

1061
01:19:53,875 --> 01:19:55,075
I owe you an apology.

1062
01:19:55,875 --> 01:19:57,675
For not believing in me or for slapping me?

1063
01:19:58,275 --> 01:20:00,275
Both.
Can you ever forgive me?

1064
01:20:03,275 --> 01:20:04,275
I'll think of a way...

1065
01:20:06,675 --> 01:20:08,075
I read about your exploits.

1066
01:20:09,475 --> 01:20:10,075
Amazing!

1067
01:20:11,075 --> 01:20:14,075
This experience made us think.
Thanks.

1068
01:20:15,475 --> 01:20:17,835
We are going to change the way we see the road.

1069
01:20:17,955 --> 01:20:20,275
...create a more efficient police force.

1070
01:20:20,475 --> 01:20:21,075
Modernise.

1071
01:20:21,275 --> 01:20:22,075
All thanks to you.

1072
01:20:22,275 --> 01:20:23,275
Thankyou sir.

1073
01:20:23,875 --> 01:20:28,275
The medal is only a symbol.
It won't get your licence back.

1074
01:20:28,675 --> 01:20:30,075
I was hoping for more...

1075
01:20:30,275 --> 01:20:30,875
Mercy?

1076
01:20:31,075 --> 01:20:31,875
Yes, that would be good.

1077
01:20:32,275 --> 01:20:35,635
We had evidence to put you in
jail for years. But you are free.

1078
01:20:35,715 --> 01:20:36,875
I'm not free. I'm on foot.

1079
01:20:37,875 --> 01:20:38,675
I understand.

1080
01:20:38,915 --> 01:20:40,875
Without a car
you are like an orphan.

1081
01:20:41,275 --> 01:20:42,475
Yes an pedestrian orphan.

1082
01:20:42,875 --> 01:20:43,675
I understand.

1083
01:20:44,475 --> 01:20:46,475
I have a solution
but I'm not sure you will like it.

1084
01:20:48,915 --> 01:20:50,675
Tell me and we'll see.

1085
01:21:01,715 --> 01:21:02,675
So are you happy or not?

1086
01:21:02,875 --> 01:21:03,475
Yes.

1087
01:21:03,875 --> 01:21:04,675
You're not happy?

1088
01:21:04,875 --> 01:21:05,875
Yes it's super.

1089
01:21:06,075 --> 01:21:09,915
I don't understand. First Grand Prix.
First grid, super car, friends,...

1090
01:21:09,995 --> 01:21:12,475
...beautiful girlfriend. What's wrong?

1091
01:21:12,875 --> 01:21:14,475
The sponsor!

1092
01:21:15,715 --> 01:21:19,315
We find him money, a car
and still he's unhappy.

1093
01:21:22,555 --> 01:21:26,475
Tell the cheerleaders to stop waving their pom-poms.
It distracts me.

1094
01:21:26,795 --> 01:21:29,475
You know what you could do
to make me happy?

1095
01:21:29,675 --> 01:21:30,475
Yeah? What?

1096
01:21:30,795 --> 01:21:34,475
Win the race! It doesn't matter a damn
which sponsor's name is on the car.

1097
01:21:35,955 --> 01:21:39,275
Ok then, Take the Champagne out of
the fridge 'cos I don't like it too cold.

1098
01:21:45,955 --> 01:21:47,915
Let's go, Daniel!

1099
01:22:53,875 --> 01:22:55,875
Subtitles by Nix 2003

